As one of the head of Hospitality training in the world, Switzerland has been a best destination for Vietnamese student lately. How is the life of a oversea student in Swiss? What should we prepare for studying abroad? That is the reason for holding the seminar “THE SWISS LIFE FOR OVERSEAS STUDENT” hosted by Vietnam Hospitality Network (VHN) and Business Hotel & Management School (BHMS). Our seminar will mention these contents:
>>> Education in Switzerland
>>> Training program of BHMS
>>> Life in Switzerland
>>> Career development after graduation in Switzerland

This seminar will give you an opportunity to listen and discuss with top experts about what you need to know when studying in Switzerland.
